        "subject": "LU-19856 ldiskfs: remove rhel7.9 ldiskfs patch series",
        "message": "LU-19856 ldiskfs: remove rhel7.9 ldiskfs patch series\n\nThe RHEL7.9 and earlier kernels are no longer supported.\n\nRemove the ldiskfs-3.10-rhel7.9.series file and all patches that\nare no longer used by this (or other) patch series. The actual\npatches under ldiskfs/kernel_patches/patches/rhel7.x may still be\nreferenced by newer kernel series, so cannot be removed wholesale.\n\nThe ./contrib/scripts/clearpatches.sh ldiskfs/kernel_patches command\nwill report which patches are no longer used by any series file.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I05edf941a2eff1865df5ce3003447c9f2a0cee44\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/63824\nReviewed-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: James Simmons <jsimmons@infradead.org>\nReviewed-by: Shaun Tancheff <shaun.tancheff@hpe.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
